<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I had the same thought. The ONLY way they could know of those details is if that boat made it. It is still ambiguous if the boy survived from the firs<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I had the same thought. The ONLY way they could know of those details is if that boat made it. It is still ambiguous if the boy survived from the first story, but the boat made it for sure.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
