		    <b>
          <a title="What&#39;s the Name of That Book???" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/19774817-solved-magical-realism-short-story-about-cuban-revolution-children-an">What&#39;s the Name o...:</a>
        </b>
      
			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/19774817-solved-magical-realism-short-story-about-cuban-revolution-children-an">SOLVED. Magical realism short story about Cuban revolution, children, and butterflies. [s]</a>
